comment: I want to thank you for sending in this game. Unlike many who send submissions, you sent a loss. This is exactly the kind of game that an individual can get the most out of -- one of his/her draws or losses. I myself did the same when I was a youth, and by continually going over games that I lost/drew, I found out what I did wrong, and resolved not to repeat them. I did go over wins as well to look for improvements, but rarely did I learn as much. BTW, I have a feeling that if the computer gives you a free queen again, it will be in trouble, because you've learned from your mistakes! Keep up the good fight.
